casebody.data:
Yvon ST JUSTE, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEUTSCHE BANK NATIONAL TRUST COMPANY, etc., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1328 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 18, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated August 22, 2017, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
